                            <p class="text-justify">The best frequent flyer program for 2022 is the Mileage Plan from Alaska Airlines. Hence it is not at all challenging to use rewards credit cards that offer miles. Try to get a credit card that best fits your lifestyle, and charge carefully on things that will boost your miles while keeping your debt to zero. </p>
